OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and sunny today, and
OL,6,Fbecoming very hot, locally
OL,7,Fexceptionally hot across the south,
OL,8,Fwith the potential for temperatures to
OL,9,Fcause significant disruption. Also
OL,10,Ffeeling humid, although onshore
OL,11,Fbreezes will keep coastal areas a
OL,12,Flittle fresher.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FDespite largely clear skies
OL,15,Fmany places will have another warm or
OL,16,Fvery warm night, especially in large
OL,17,Ftowns and cities, with the humid
OL,18,Fconditions persisting.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
