OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FGenerally sunny and very
OL,6,Fwarm or hot. Breezier than recently,
OL,7,Fespecially along the coast which will
OL,8,Fkeep temperatures cooler than inland
OL,9,Fand bring a chance of mist and low
OL,10,Fcloud.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FHot or
OL,13,Fvery hot Friday, thereafter
OL,14,Ftemperatures decreasing. Sunny spells
OL,15,FFriday and Saturday, with a chance of
OL,16,Fisolated thunderstorms. Cloudier
OL,17,FSunday and possibly patchy light rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
